2. Key Technical Concepts:
   - Spring Boot + Spring AI `@Tool`/`@ToolParam` annotations for AI tool registration
   - `LoggingToolCallback` wraps all tools — if `approvalService != null` it emits `TYPE_TOOL_PENDING` before execution
   - `ToolApprovalService` — `ConcurrentHashMap<String, CompletableFuture<Boolean>>` for blocking approval
   - Server-Sent Events (SSE) streaming with `StreamChunk` record types
