   - LCS (Longest Common Subsequence) diff algorithm in TypeScript for git-style line diff rendering
   - `TYPE_TOOL_PENDING` JSON enriched with extra fields (`operation`, `path`, `oldContent`, `newContent`) for file ops — frontend detects `operation` field to switch `ToolApprovalCard` to diff view

3. Files and Code Sections:

   - **`src/main/java/com/programmersdiary/aidaemon/skills/FileEditTool.java`** (NEW)
